{"tid":1185440,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國多個駐中大使館下半旗   白宮稱悼念槍擊案死難者","createTime":"2019-06-04T09:24:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-04T09:25:34.000Z","uid":184679,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"66c625bb3d9f399321b2c01c9e03df47e76625ac","tid":1185440,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T09:24:07.000Z","msg":"今天（4日）是六四事件30周年，美國在北京駐華大使館，以至香港、廣州、上海、成都、瀋陽、武漢的總領事館均下半旗。據白宮新聞稿指，美國全球使領館均在今日下半旗，是悼念上周五（31日）維珍尼亞州槍擊案死難者。<br />\n<br />\n據報道，美國全球使領館，在今日（4日）均下半旗，向5月31日維珍尼亞州槍擊案死難者致哀。槍擊案是政府職員，懷疑不滿被解僱，在市政中心無差別殺人，造成12人死亡，4人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.modia.com.hk/2019/06/04/129321/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%9A%E5%80%8B%E9%A7%90%E8%8F%AF%E5%A4%A7%E4%BD%BF%E9%A4%A8%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%8A%E6%97%97-%E7%99%BD%E5%AE%AE%E7%A8%B1%E6%82%BC%E5%BF%B5%E6%A7%8D%E6%93%8A%E6%A1%88%E6%AD%BB%E9%9B%A3/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.modia.com.hk%2F2019%2F06%2F04%2F129321%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%2580%258B%25E9%25A7%2590%25E8%258F%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E4%25BD%25BF%25E9%25A4%25A8%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%258A%25E6%2597%2597-%25E7%2599%25BD%25E5%25AE%25AE%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E6%2582%25BC%25E5%25BF%25B5%25E6%25A7%258D%25E6%2593%258A%25E6%25A1%2588%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E9%259B%25A3%2F&d=nhC78NoCA6QB0w8lKR9CgsdEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=90bc533c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.modia.com.hk/2019/06/04/129321/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%9A%E5%80%8B%E9%A7%90%E8%8F%AF%E5%A4%A7%E4%BD%BF%E9%A4%A8%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%8A%E6%97%97-%E7%99%BD%E5%AE%AE%E7%A8%B1%E6%82%BC%E5%BF%B5%E6%A7%8D%E6%93%8A%E6%A1%88%E6%AD%BB%E9%9B%A3/</a>"},{"pid":"2a0de609203b6f5f97a442c36dc360a218e9eabd","tid":1185440,"uid":244332,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T09:25:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BSSpYPs.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBSSpYPs.gif&h=88b0fdfb&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}